# Legacy repo-scripts layer — DATA and EVIDENCE are NEVER tracked. Only code
# and config are committed.
#
# raw/     = immutable verbatim mysqldumps (private; PII and other sensitive material)
# parsed/  = extracted NDJSON (rebuildable from raw)
# reports/ = ingest/seal audit JSONs — operational evidence of the dump ingests;
#            their home is the maintainers' private repository's evidence
#            directory, not this public repo. Only the .gitkeep is tracked so
#            the directory exists for a run's output.

raw/
parsed/
reports/*
!reports/.gitkeep
